getVirtualType

IVirtualType getVirtualType(java.lang.String name,
                            java.lang.String namespace)
Locates an virtual type given its name and its namespace.

Parameters:
name - The virtual type's name; must not be null
namespace - the virtual type's namespace; must not be null
Returns:
the located virtual type or null if the virtual type name and namespace pair was not located in the virtual type registry

getAllVirtualTypes

IVirtualType[] getAllVirtualTypes()
Locates all virtual types. Abstract types will be excluded.

Returns:
all virtual types; never null

Parameters:

Returns:
